#+begin_src elisp :exports both
(defun solve-6-1 (data)
  (let ((stack '())(counter 0))
    (dotimes
        (i (length data))
      (progn
        (push (elt data i) stack)
        (cond
         ((< (length stack) 4) nil)
         ((equal (length stack) 4)( if (equal (length stack) (length (remove-duplicates stack)))(return (cons stack (+ i 1))) (setq stack (butlast stack)))))
        ))))

(solve-6-1 dummy1)
#+end_src

#+RESULTS:
: ((109 113 112 106) . 7)

#+begin_src elisp :exports both
(solve-6-1 input)
#+end_src

#+RESULTS:
: ((100 106 114 104) . 1042)
